Stephanie Kalu (amụrụ na 8 Mee 1993) bụ onye America a mụrụ na Naijirịa na-agba ọsọ nke maara nke ọma na mita 100, mita 200 na mita 4 x 100. Ọ nọchitere anya Naijirịa n'ọtụtụ egwuregwu gụnyere 2012 World Junior Championships in Athletics, 2013 Summer Universiade na 2013 World Championships in Atletics
Ọ ga-asọ mpi na 2015 World Championships in Athletics mgbe ọ na-anọchite anya Naijirịa.
